<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/202412-i-m-just-noticing-that-an-additional-book">I&#39;m just noticing that an additional book was written nearly forty years after Canticle by Walter Miller and a co-author. Is this one of those sci-fi sequels I should just ignore, a la Rama II? Can Canticle be treated as a standalone novel?</a>
