<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Canticle can certainly stand on its own. I read the sequel may years ago, but I don&apos;t remember it well, and critical commentary is not kind to the pos<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Canticle can certainly stand on its own. I read the sequel may years ago, but I don't remember it well, and critical commentary is not kind to the posthumous work. I read Canticle often as part of a course I teach, and I never, ever get tired of it. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
