<div id="review_4489513810" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4489513810" />
    <a title="Lena" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/120939577-lena"><img alt="Lena" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1599423212p2/120939577.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4489513810?book_show_action=true">Jan 26, 2022</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lena" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lena" href="/user/show/120939577-lena">Lena</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9785170994694" href="/book/show/35719021">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4489513810" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6642691126738968164">Cruel, but realistic demonstration of the famous saying that we doomed to repeat our history. Apocalyptic chronicle shows the ugliest sides of society and human nature. If it wasn&apos;t so religious I would liked it even more.</span>
  <span id="freeText6642691126738968164" style="display:none">Cruel, but realistic demonstration of the famous saying that we doomed to repeat our history. Apocalyptic chronicle shows the ugliest sides of society and human nature. If it wasn't so religious I would liked it even more.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6642691126738968164" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


